ZH: 我每天早上起床的第一件事就是祷告。
EN: The first thing I do every morning when I wake up is pray.

ZH: 他们在教堂里共同祷告。
EN: They pray together in the church.

ZH: 我经常在晚上睡觉前祷告。
EN: I often pray before going to bed at night.

ZH: 她沉浸在沉思和祷告之中。
EN: She is immersed in contemplation and prayer.

ZH: 他向上帝祷告，让自己在难关中找到力量。
EN: He prays to God to find strength in tough times.

ZH: 祷告是与上帝交流的一种方式。
EN: Prayer is a way to communicate with God.

ZH: 我们需要在困难时刻寻求祷告的支持。
EN: We need to seek the support of prayer in difficult times.

ZH: 我们每天都应该花一些时间与上帝祷告。
EN: We should take some time every day to pray to God.

ZH: 她在困惑时常会找到答案，通过祷告。
EN: She often finds answers through prayer when she is confused.

ZH: 教堂里有一个专门的区域可以祷告。
EN: There is a dedicated area for prayer in the church.

